<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-78-0865 </DOCNO><TEXT>After a general discussion of the energy-political importance of combinedheat and power generation systems, and in particular modular cogenerationpower plants, the fields of application and design variations of cogenerationplants are presented. The important role of system design as a decisivefactor determining the economic efficiency of modular cogeneration plantsis discussed together with some other influencing factors, e.g. energyprices and price trends, and servicing. The operating experience of tenyears of cogeneration systems is presented in summary form.</TEXT></DOC>